{"tid":143850,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"剛力彩芽出演動畫《冰菓》真人版電影女主角 2ch網民一片哀嚎崩潰","createTime":"2017-03-05T03:28:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T13:28:15.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dd7a2b0176bf2648505cb66f3fad9ee7efa51420","tid":143850,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T03:28:04.000Z","msg":"由米澤穗信所著的系列推理小說中，以同名原作改編成的電視動畫《冰菓》，自 2012 年播出以來，無疑已經成為超人氣的校園動畫之一，故事圍繞在校園生活的消極少年折木奉太郎，與個性相反、充滿好奇心又積極的少女千反田愛瑠在即將倒閉的古典社相遇了，兩人展開了一段互相對抗又互相了解的有趣相處過程。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/52074/56d98a93b806f.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F52074%2F56d98a93b806f.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=a1389e47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼而就在這幾天的大新聞，那就是角川決定要將《冰菓》、《春夏事件簿》拍成真人版電影。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/52074/56d98bda01f96.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F52074%2F56d98bda01f96.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=2a9287c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼今天更震撼的消息出來了，那就是萬眾矚目的男女主角演員人選公布！首先是相當惹人憐愛的女主角「千反田愛瑠」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/52074/56d98d2a0ed7e.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F52074%2F56d98d2a0ed7e.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=6251f762&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://g4.ykimg.com/1100641F464BD8E8E426B400196E53081955BF-4EF0-4E6C-BF28-0301E920C7B8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fg4.ykimg.com%2F1100641F464BD8E8E426B400196E53081955BF-4EF0-4E6C-BF28-0301E920C7B8&h=b2c32874&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/52074/56d98cdf7fa1c.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F52074%2F56d98cdf7fa1c.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=30bd753c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼由 23 歲女演員兼歌手剛力彩芽飾演。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/52074/56d98cfd8c8cc.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F52074%2F56d98cfd8c8cc.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=39fe9de9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼極度聰明和崇尚節能的男主角「折木奉太郎」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/52074/56d98d81e3c3c.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F52074%2F56d98d81e3c3c.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=0b64b112&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼將由傑尼斯偶像團體 Sexy Zone 當中 19 歲成員佐藤勝利飾演。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/52074/56d98dac8873d.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F52074%2F56d98dac8873d.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=db0ccbba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這個消息一出，立刻引起日本鄉民在 2ch 上【悲報】，網友紛紛吐槽說：「剛力彩芽演高中生根本無理！」、「為什麼要讓頭髮這麼短的剛力彩芽演千反田？剛力彩芽去演御坂美琴都感覺比較適合」、「公布主演名單之後，這部電影立刻暴死」、「光看演員就已經確認失敗了」、「剛力彩芽讓我超崩潰」、「為什麼要毀掉我最喜歡的青春故事...」。<br />\n<br />\n▼男主角折木奉太郎確定由佐藤勝利飾演，也引起推特出現一片哀嚎。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/52074/56d98f274dc93.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F52074%2F56d98f274dc93.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=10bd047f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n許多網友認為如果是橋本環奈來演千反田愛瑠，或許多少還能夠還原千反田愛瑠那閃閃發亮的眼神，剛力彩芽的長相比起來畢竟太老成，跟高中生的感覺實在有頗大的差距，你看完這兩位主演也感覺到崩潰了嗎？<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/52074/56d98f899e158.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F52074%2F56d98f899e158.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=ef5175ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2645921fd062ee8207c2130e5e5e1f1ae39c0906","tid":143850,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T03:35:21.000Z","msg":"之前古書堂已經比人屌撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f967e26b667eb544ed5c7c37d45f691862b0f498","tid":143850,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T03:38:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前古書堂已經比人屌撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仆佢個街仲要真係短頭髮"},{"pid":"4cd9fc9a2e971614ef4ebe3c2b93ed97073f6fb8","tid":143850,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T03:59:53.000Z","msg":"條仔好撚柒喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f8dbcfb5116dd1bf8df970167755970879360b","tid":143850,"uid":7311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:02:14.000Z","msg":"剛牙仲係歌手？<br />\n<br />\n佢首出道作<br />\n峯岸南唱得仲好聽過佢"},{"pid":"ec5aa2cc55db924972c571154252c6928c99592a","tid":143850,"uid":5055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:17:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd15c6c3cc6c0c9d7c81bea45f8f21de84ba0f3b","tid":143850,"uid":64744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:20:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a49be4e19907a7672c7fd1d5b5e27fb32be81c3","tid":143850,"uid":33176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:26:39.000Z","msg":"幾時拍真人版筋肉人"},{"pid":"e7e1b7b07c012700b03679987